{"tid":1857780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多區區議員促封關 擬發起口岸「和你塞」抗議","createTime":"2020-02-02T10:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T02:55:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa343fb952cd790991423dcc6eb77f0e9cd4c2a","tid":1857780,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2ch4eAyeEq5a4hBVZd.l5Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9Mzk3/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-02/68a4a810-4590-11ea-bcad-7eb4347a9982\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2ch4eAyeEq5a4hBVZd.l5Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9Mzk3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-02%2F68a4a810-4590-11ea-bcad-7eb4347a9982&h=e549c954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社會不少聲音質疑政府針對武漢肺炎防疫不力，18區區議會聯席會議今(2日)舉行記者會，出席區議員均繫上白絲帶，指全力聲援和配合醫護界罷工，警告政府若繼續拒絕封關，不排除會發動到各口岸進行「和你塞」抗議行動。<br />\n<br />\n身兼輪任召集人的屯門區議會主席陳樹英指，民調顯示接近80%市民支持封關，指內地不少城市都封城，香港封關不會構成歧視，又比較香港和澳門的防疫工作，指香港有社區爆發迹象，若港再多一宗確診而特首仍拒封關，將發起到羅湖等各關口進行「和你塞」抗議行動。<br />\n<br />\n曾任公立醫院註冊護士的西貢區議員陳緯烈指部分區議員會配合醫護界行動，例如在各區設立街站等，現時醫護界頻崩潰，冀市民體諒罷工的決定。<br />\n<br />\n至於政府多次設立隔離設施和指定流感診所均引起居民反對，甚至觸發衝突，多區區議員批評政府事前無做任何諮詢，中西區區議員葉錦龍擔心設立指定診所會令社區爆發提早出現，也憂慮醫療資源為內地人而設。"},{"pid":"ad806b7cd937034d20ff27c3ecfbd1d4af6b6e06","tid":1857780,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:36:08.000Z","msg":"關口搞野，俾人乘亂過關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa2da5fbd218b5c31ac953c1562026f9d736d94","tid":1857780,"uid":295548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:36:31.000Z","msg":"《天滅中共賦》<br />\n<br />\n共黨臣民 作惡多端<br />\n外侵諸邦 內屠義士<br />\n赤匪所至 寸草不生<br />\n禍國殃民 血債累累<br />\n習妖維尼 逆天而行<br />\n自立為帝 天怒人怨<br />\n庚子伊始 天譴將臨<br />\n大仙報夢 國運已盡<br />\n共黨治下 必有七患<br />\n正月武肺 播毒中原<br />\n二月流感 飛禽盡亡<br />\n三月地震 血流成河<br />\n四月豬瘟 百物騰升<br />\n五月飢荒 易子而食<br />\n六月內戰 析骸而爨<br />\n七月水災 長江決堤<br />\n炎共將亡 水德當立<br />\n歲在庚子 天滅中共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCW3BCS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCW3BCS.jpg&h=64a71671&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"293534a75182efdde659bb5de741acc38a3158cc","tid":1857780,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家幫手推一推，正個評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足裝備抗沙士：護目鏡（型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1857672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1857672</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9LtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=f0c4f187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家幫手正評，避免沉底"},{"pid":"5f135f16b3dad96119c014c5f34f01985b88fc15","tid":1857780,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:37:43.000Z","msg":"嚟啦嚟啦，反正home office唔使點做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972c71022838c3ae4e297e1c33ffd43f3a11e997","tid":1857780,"uid":199838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea25900a8e5a10a94a7b3483415aff5acabd0eee","tid":1857780,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:55:51.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac